N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 136.3 - Supervision

State Regulations

It shall be the policy of State departments and agencies to
have supervision of extra-service help provided by regular supervisory
personnel unless circumstances are exceptional. Notes
